            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>去年登场的 AION Y PLUS 凭著实用的车箱空间设计得到不少车主支持，最近广汽埃安的香港代理引入全新的 AION V 电动车，作为品牌在香港发售的最新中型 SUV 车款，新车以实用设计、宽敞的空间及齐全的安全设备作招徕，而且售价亦非常亲民，相当适合家庭用户代步。</p><p>由外形来看，AION V 没有像其他电动车刻意营造未来感，把车身设计得特别圆滑或采用条状大灯突显科幻感。相反，厂方指新车<span style="font-weight: 400;">采用「刃影势能」的设计语言，外形更接近传统电油汽车，方正的车身加上头尾硬朗锐利的线条，搭配」龙爪」元素的 LED 头尾灯，外形更加顺眼，没有标奇立异的感觉。车身长度为 4605mm，轴距为 2775mm，大小和 Audi Q4-e-tron、Mercedes Benz EQB 或 Tesla Model Y 相若，后排达 1040mm 的腿部空间提供极之充裕的 Leg room 及 Head room，宽敞舒适的乘坐空间具备极高实用性。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303930" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115803-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115803-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115803.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120854-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120854-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120854.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120335-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120335-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120335.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120347-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120347-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120347.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303946 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_121709-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_121709-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_121709.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">性能方面，AION V 提供两个不同版本选择，Premium 和 Luxury 版本采用容量为 64.5kWh 和 75.26kWh 的磷酸铁锂弹匣电池 2.0，续航力分别为 505km 和 602km（NEDC 标准），相信满足不同用户对长途驾驶的需求。动力则采用前置永磁同步电机，最大扭力为 240Nm，而两个版本分别可提供 135kW 或 150kW 的动力输出，配合广汽的 400V 电控系统，无论是市区起步还是高速巡航，都具备有力而稳定的行车表现。此外，AION V 的 DC 充电功率分别为 150kW / 180kW，</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">支持 3C 快充技术，最快可于 16 分钟把电池由 30% 充至 80%，充电时间得以缩短。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_113950-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_113950-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_113950.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114330-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114330-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114330.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全景天幕备有电动太阳帘，功能齐全</p><p>虽然 AION V 最大扭矩只得 240N.m，跟市场上如 MG ZS EV、Audi Q4-e-tron 动力相若，而测试的 Luxury 版本（150kW / 201 匹）时明显感觉到它的加速能力比起数字上更强，虽说是家庭车型但加速能力绝不下于高性能 SUV 油车，灯前起步或爬头亦绰绰有余。随车设有不同的驾驶模式，驾驶者可以轻松设定軚盘、电门、刹车的软硬程度而提供不同的驾驶体验，想舒适地在市区代步、或在高速公路上舒展一下，都能带来不同的乐趣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303936 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122200-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122200-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122200.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122136-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122136-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122136.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ADiGo 智能系统提供前后方防撞预警、车道维持、盲点侦测、紧急刹车等多项安全保护。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303939 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114035-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114035-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114035.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>一如其他同级家庭 SUV，AION V 悬挂亦采用偏软的舒适为主取向，试车时在观塘道、将军澳隧道至布袋澳路段的路面滤震表现不俗，4.6 米的车身长度亦提供很高的灵活性，不论是切线、窄路调头都算得上就手。笔记自己就喜欢 AION V 特大的前挡风玻璃，较高的坐姿视野更加宽广，而且 A / B 柱盲点亦不算严重，比起不少国产车设计优胜。要数美中不足的是 AION V 的车箱隔音效果一般，驾驶时能听到颇明显的路噪，如果对宁静有要求的人士可能要再强化一下车门隔音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303924 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114055-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114055-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114055.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AION V 设有驾驶员监测系统，若果分心、不集中、玩电话便会马上作出警示，此外，随车亦设有 360 泊车系统，去到陌生环境泊车亦可提高信心。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303937 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_123010-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_123010-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_123010.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303923 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114016-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114016-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114016.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前座设有一个 50W 无线充电板，如果能让前座乘客同时使用相信更加吸引</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在安全方面，AION V 以全方位防护作卖点，配备前排中置气袋，防止前排驾驶者与乘客碰撞，而 2.3 米超长车厢两侧更设有特别设计的气囊，确保后排乘客的安全。另一方面，跟车的智能和安全科技亦是 AION V 的一大亮点。新车提供超过 20 项安全及辅助功能，除了常见的 ACC、EBD、ESP、LDW、BSD、LKA、更提供同级车少见的驾驶员监测系统、前后碰撞预警、侧窗帘式气囊、倒车横穿交通辅助及开门预警等，加上 360 泊车，功能于 20 万多的车款中算是非常齐全。车内配备 14.6 吋轻触中控屏与 8.88 吋数码仪表，但是语音功能暂时只能支援英文及普通话而不是大家常用的广东话，车载地图亦需要连接手机 CarPlay 才可使用，希望稍后时间可以透过 OTA 追力其他功能。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303925 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114136-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114136-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114136.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AION V 手枕下的迷你雪柜真心够冻，可以放置 4 瓶小支装水，热天消暑一流</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303928 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120946_-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120946_-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120946_.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲夏天可以设至最低 -15 度，而冬天则可以设定至 50 度，想要热饮亦不成问题</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303926 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114434-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114434-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_114434.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左后方乘客位与 HYPTEC HT 一样备有超实净的金属炼较餐桌，放置笔电砰板工作亦非常稳固</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303927 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120655-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120655-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_120655.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲尾箱下方暗格收装了后备轮呔，对于要驾驶长途车的朋友来说更有安全感</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">前作 AION Y PLUS 曾以全平坐位可供车中泊作卖点，而 5 座位的 AION V Premium 和 Luxury 分别选用人造皮及真皮冷暖通风座椅，前座两张座椅更具备 8 点按摩功能，而后排座椅可按比例调后最 137 度，随车设有一键躺平功能，只需把前座的头枕移除即可变身成一张超过 2 米的巨型零重力座椅，如坐梳化般的感觉不论是休息或睡觉都十分舒服，配合特大全景天窗开扬感更高。</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">配置方面，AION V 前座设有一个 50W 无线充电板、中排配备可调节 -15 至 50 度的雪柜，在测试当日下午约 28 度仍可把支装水雪到冰冻，</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303941 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122116-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122116-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_122116.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在智能座舱面板可以设定前方两张按摩座位的按摩模式，虽然力度比不上专业按摩椅，不过在路途上放松一下已经很不错</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115457-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115457-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115457.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303921" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115433-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115433-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115433.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在中控面板设有一键大床功能，不过就要用户先行拆掉前座头枕才能完全平放，一键躺平功能其间会提醒用户，如果不拆头枕降到一定位置便会卡住。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303920" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115250-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115250-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250414_115250.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303944 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250417225016-602x580.jpg" alt="" width="602" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250417225016-602x580.jpg 602w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250417225016.jpg 934w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 602px" /></p><p>查询: APMG (3591 9336)</p><br /><b>
